gw (0.3.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Use XDG_DATA_DIRS to find data files.
  * Remove Notebook and related widgets.
  * Leds now has separate name and color properties.
  * Ignore non-ev3dev Leds.
  * Updates for kernel changes (ev3dev kernel level 9).
  * Add get_power_supply method to DeviceManager.
  * PowerSupply class now uses enums for some properties instead of strings.
  * Add 16x16 icons.
  * Add Cpu namespace for getting cpu info.
  * GtkApp now only shows one screen at a time. Use EV3DEVKIT_SCREEN environment
    variable to load different screen types.
  * Increase the default font size.
  * Add virtual screens for PiStorms and EVB.
  * Add Stack widget.
  * Change API version to 0.3.
  * Remove dependency on libgee (improves performance).
  * Add InputDialog class. (Thanks @ensonic).

 -- David Lechner <david@lechnology.com>  Tue, 15 Dec 2015 12:18:11 -0600

